🎤 Most Asked Interview Questions

Q1. What is Catalyst Optimizer?

Answer

Catalyst is Spark SQL's query optimizer. It analyzes and rewrites logical plans into optimized physical execution plans.


---

Q2. What does explain(True) display?

Answer

It shows:

Parsed Logical Plan

Analyzed Logical Plan

Optimized Logical Plan

Physical Execution Plan



---

Q3. Why is Catalyst important?

Answer

It automatically optimizes queries, reducing execution time without requiring manual query rewrites.


